  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to kidletime</title>

    <para>
      KIdleTime is used to report the idle time of users and the system. It is
useful not only for determining the current idle time of the PC, but also
for getting notified upon idle time events, such as custom timeouts or user
activity.
    </para>

    &lfs120_checked;

    <important>
      <para>
        This package is extracted from the KF5 set of packages.  If <xref
linkend="kf5-frameworks"/> is built, do <emphasis role="bold">NOT</emphasis>
also build this package as presented here.
      </para>
    </important>

